nodes.title: For Manual Mode 1
widgets_values: Right click on the image, open in mask editor, select add mask, make the mask, and then click save to node
hand, high quality, highly detailed, highest quality 4k, 8k, 32k

Prompt for what you are trying to change. Some adjustments made be made with quality words.

-Mask Switch: select where the mask will pull from for inpainting. 1 is for using the mask editor in the image loader manually.

-Fast Bypasser: Only turn on the models you are using, this will keep vram usage lower.

-Upscale Factor: When "Enable Upscale by Factor" is enabled you select the upscale factor here. (whole image)

-Fill_Holes: Enable when masking areas that might need cutouts, like buttons etc"
